1. Which of the following scenarios represents a suitable regression target variable?


a. Classifying whether an email is spam or not.
b. Identifying whether a patient has a certain medical condition.
c. Predicting the type of flower species based on petal length and width.
d. Estimating the time it takes to complete a marathon race.

Correct! d
2. In which of the following situations is regression the most appropriate technique?
a. Forecasting the price of a house based on its features.
b. Predicting whether a customer will buy a product.
c. Categorizing images of animals into different species.
d. Determining the sentiment (positive/negative) of a movie review.

Correct! a
